uber诽谤的应对状况，向当事人收取约116万日元的和解金</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Buispo！公布针对所属VTuber的诽谤行为的回应情况。从相关人员处收取了约116万日元的和解金” - P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vspo-has-disclosed-the-status-of-response-to-the-slander-of-affiliating-vtuber-recovered-a-settlement-of-approx-1-16m-yen-from-the-offender/embed/#?secret=nRaWMZRvKO#?secret=k7IkuuQYqE" data-secret="k7IkuuQYqE" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="3mVGCIaaLU"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-operator-cover-corporation-completed-legal-action-against-5-roundup-blogs-and-others-in-2023/">2023年完成对涵盖Hololive生产运营的5个综合网站的法律措施</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“针对涵盖 Hololive Production 运营的 5 个综合网站的法律措施将于 2023 年完成” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-operator-cover-corporation-completed-legal-action-against-5-roundup-blogs-and-others-in-2023/embed/#?secret=XeMUf2Mlck#?secret=3mVGCIaaLU" data-secret="3mVGCIaaLU" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="coVJOpK1fo"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hoshimachi-suisei-overlapping-with-some-listeners-of-vtuber-group-nijisanji/">星町水成VTuber组合“虹三路”的诽谤 有报道称部分观众重叠</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“水成星町的诽谤者：有报道称，VTuber 团体“Nijisanji”的部分观众重叠” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/slanderer-against-hoshimachi-suisei-overlapping-with-some-listeners-of-vtu